	<text>
		<body xml:lang="en">
			<div>

	<pb n="0001" facs="liv_002313_0001"/><!--pb/@n='1r'-->
<lb/><p rend="center"><placeName>Burnbank Road</placeName></p>
<lb/><p rend="center"><space extent="2" unit="chars"/><placeName>Hamilton</placeName></p>
<lb/><p rend="center"><space extent="1" unit="words"/><space extent="1" unit="chars"/>25 May 1865 </p>
<lb/>
<lb/><p rend="no-indent">My Dear <persName>D<hi rend="sup underline">r</hi> Tidman</persName></p>
<lb/><p>I have been rather 
<lb/>surprised at finding 
<lb/>that several good 
<lb/>people have been 
<lb/>made uneasy by 
<lb/>the aspersions of 
<lb/>that beastly fellow 
<lb/><persName>Burton</persName> against 
<lb/>the missionaries 
<lb/>on the West Coast<reg>.</reg>
<lb/>My answer to them 
<lb/>has been that so 
<lb/>much care is exercised 

	<pb n="0002" facs="liv_002313_0002"/><!--pb/@n='1v'-->
<lb/>in the selection that 
<lb/>no uneasiness need 
<lb/>be felt, and I know 
<lb/>them to be generally 
<lb/>devoted and upright 
<lb/>men, but it is 
<lb/>probable that more 
<lb/>are in doubt than 
<lb/>have come to my 
<lb/>knowledge. One 
<lb/>cannot defile 
<lb/>himself by touching 
<lb/>such as <persName>Burton</persName>
<lb/>who seems to be a 
<lb/>moral idiot. His 
<lb/>conduct in <placeName>Africa</placeName>
<lb/>was so bad that 
<lb/>it cannot be spoken of 

	<pb n="0003" facs="liv_002313_0003"/><!--pb/@n='2r'-->
<lb/>without disgust - 
<w>system-<lb break="no"/>atically</w> wicked - and 
<lb/>impure, and untruthful. 
<lb/>Would it not be 
<lb/>better to invite <persName>M<hi rend="sup underline">r</hi> 
<lb/>Moffat</persName> home for 
<lb/>a year just to shew 
<lb/>people what a 
<lb/>missionary is - I 
<lb/>would not like 
<lb/>him to be worked 
<lb/>to death, but his 
<lb/>presence would do 
<lb/>more good here 
<lb/>than he doing out 
<lb/>at <placeName>Kuruman</placeName> now<reg>.</reg>
<lb/>He could get his 
<lb/>revised New Testa
<lb/>ment printed here 

	<pb n="0004" facs="liv_002313_0004"/><!--pb/@n='2v'-->
<lb/>and actually save 
<lb/>time. I venture 
<lb/>to throw this out to 
<lb/>you as a hint of 
<lb/>which you may 
<lb/>be disposed or not 
<lb/>to take advantage - 
<lb/>and which you need 
<lb/>not trouble yourself 
<lb/>to answer<reg>.</reg></p>
<lb/><p rend="no-indent"><space extent="3" unit="chars"/>I am &amp;c </p>
<lb/><p rend="no-indent"><persName>David Livingstone</persName></p>
			
